            <fullName>BulkSelectBundleComponent_179Ws000000ZkBG</fullName>
            <description>Apply the SAME component change to EVERY instance of a bundle product on a quote in one deterministic pass. Use when the user says &apos;all&apos; / &apos;every&apos;, or when there are multiple instances of the same bundle. SELECT needs productRelatedComponentId; DESELECT needs childProductId. All-or-nothing: if any instance is blocked by bundle rules, nothing is saved. Reports per-bundle results. Cannot create new products or delete arbitrary records.</description>
